own the account of the Kasztner story related to the Brand Mission in Hungary in the period of the Holocaust (a year ago).  My friend, Emanuel (Manny) Mandel and his father Cantor Yehudah Mandel, formerly of Logan, Philadelphia, Israel, various camps in w
